2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses autonomous navigation. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper employs physically founded motion priors. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper may use machine learning techniques for motion estimation. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper deals with controlling the motion of a system (camera egomotion).
